title: Lesser Known Ramen Varieties | "Ramen Street" | Japan Video Travel Guide | Hidden Japan
description: I take a stroll along Kobe's "Ramen Kaido" - an area with hundreds of ramen shops serving noodles of every variety - and try some varieties that are gaining popularity in Japan. If you've never tried tsukemen or tori-paitan, check out the video. This is all a 40 minute train ride from Osaka.
